{"tid":964271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（估國家）【咁着數？】抽中大獎放有薪年假1年 真相係......","createTime":"2019-01-01T07:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T09:48:55.000Z","uid":54337,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"49d2ac2b58903dd44f6c68f054791b644461989e","tid":964271,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T07:53:51.000Z","msg":"【咁着數？】抽中大獎放有薪年假1年 真相係......<br />\n<br />\n上海一間公司日前舉辦年會，一名「幸運」女員工抽中「超級大獎」，其獲獎照在網上被瘋傳，見她拿着大大的獎品紙板，上寫道「上海辦公室年會特等獎帶薪年假一年」，令許多網民羨慕不已，但原來這獎品是內有玄機。<br />\n<br />\n因為這個特等獎雖寫着「帶薪年假一年」，但原來是有「使用期限」，有眼尖網民在照片右下角發現，帶薪年假有效期只到2018年12月31日，但頒獎日期是2018年12月28日，換言之，得獎女員工只得29、30及31共有3天有薪年假，而且這3天本身就是中國元旦假期，女員工其實甚麼也沒得到。"},{"pid":"62c9e9742849cfe84846d2035f684ab347c89421","tid":964271,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T07:54:07.000Z","msg":"網民們紛紛留言：「放心吧，馬上就過年了」、「愚人節嗎？」、「有效期笑死我了」、「哪間公司？老闆很幽默啊」、「最終解釋權歸本公司所有」。"},{"pid":"f339bcab5ca5e83617382ffedeebffdf6c11d0a9","tid":964271,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T07:54:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181231/59090355\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181231%2F59090355&d=AJX8bMqZTjfy%2B7WImQUbqHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=44518bb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181231%2F59090355&h=673fff0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181231/59090355</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181231/large/1546246469_1287.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181231%2Flarge%2F1546246469_1287.jpg&h=327cc71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181231/large/1546246469_1287.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181231%2Flarge%2F1546246469_1287.jpg&d=AJX8bMqZTjfy%2B7WImQUbqHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=3833f3c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181231/large/1546246469_1287.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"4630cb6a361a6e3d6fb8efcf861a15c19a067ac5","tid":964271,"uid":85629,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T08:12:07.000Z","msg":"支那豬老闆果然是賤"},{"pid":"42d6bf899e21e4f404494f1bdecd68e5f5520fd1","tid":964271,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T08:14:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8dbbeda67927e01863e944e33ad8e8f648c353c9","tid":964271,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T08:28:18.000Z","msg":"咁撚閪，最初我以為係港資<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbca1b668577e5775eb0293bfee3d5ac60dd7d1f","tid":964271,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:29:46.000Z","msg":"中國"},{"pid":"a1ef336a52c2211d2a0d67aa745e69e31cc56200","tid":964271,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8dbbeda67927e01863e944e33ad8e8f648c353c9","tid":964271,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T08:28:18.000Z","msg":"咁撚閪，最初我以為係港資<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:42:44.000Z","msg":"港資咪又係學大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84676c7df63b1eb6af3dc72702ba6e7541b86e56","tid":964271,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:48:55.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" clas